{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022640/extras/separet1Flipped.png?t=1670834395\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022640/extras/steam2.jpg?t=1670834395\" /><br>A distant past echoes through planet Syro, while its ruined landscapes are being corrupted by a mysterious force.<br><br>You, as the Seeker, will make use of a lost technology to engage in combat and explore a vast, evocative world.<br><br>XTAL is a stylish mix of action and exploration with a fast combat system that combines TPS, Hack \u2018n\u2019 Slash and Bullet Hell elements with a vibrant art style inspired by French Comics.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022640/extras/steam3.jpg?t=1670834395\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tightly tuned controls. Jump, dash and slash your way through deadly foes.<br></li><li>Fight your enemies with a blend of melee and powerful magic bullets.<br></li><li>Aiming is key! Find and shoot at your enemies' Weak Spots to deal massive damage.<br></li><li>Use your movement to dodge hundreds of bullets.<br></li><li>Explore an arcane, ruined world and discover the truth behind an ancient technology.<br></li><li>Use new abilities to reach previously inaccessible places.<br></li><li>Upgrade your arsenal, learn new skills and customize your equipment to create the perfect strategy.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022640/extras/SteamPage.gif?t=1670834395\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022640/extras/separet1.png?t=1670834395\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022640/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1670834395","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store